Norm-conserving pseudopotential for Ni including semicore
states in valence, gipaw reconstruction with two projectors
in p and d channels.

This pseudopotential has been used to calculate XAS
spectra in NiO in the absence of a core-hole in the
final state using the XSPECTRA code.

Results have been published in :

"Intrinsic charge transfer gap in NiO from Ni K-edge x-ray 
absorption spectroscopy",
C. Gougoussis, M. Calandra, A. Seitsonen, Ch. Brouder, A. Shukla, and F. Mauri
Phys. Rev. B 79, 045118 (2009) 
http://link.aps.org/doi/10.1103/PhysRevB.79.045118
